-- SEC Drops Inquiry of Ex-AIG Executive Joseph Cassano, His Attorneys Say
-- David Scheer
-- 2010-06-16T22:31:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-16/sec-drops-probe-into-ex-aig-executive-joseph-cassano-his-attorneys-say.html

          
          
             The U.S. Securities and Exchange
Commission has closed an investigation of former American
International Group Inc. executive Joseph Cassano, his attorneys
said in a statement today.  
 “We think they realized that our client acted in good
faith, kept his superiors informed, and was honest with
investors,” said F. Joseph Warin and Jim Walden of the law firm
Gibson, Dunn & Crutcher LLP in the statement.  
